core":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"逾千名中國間諜家人被習近平威脅,被迫離美 <br />\n華春瑩：相由心生，希望美國不要把所有人都看成研究員"},{"pid":"a743ad3517ded9c2f69de2c6d5ff87f301ce0ae0","tid":2310571,"uid":267494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:05:46.000Z","msg":"乜佢都知相由心生？<br />\n支那人成個樣都賊眉賊眼<br />\n又多偷呃拐騙<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226ad437de525a07b6a29c0890ad8d0c0feaa79f","tid":2310571,"uid":258948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:14:03.000Z","msg":"家陣華春瑩即係話中國人樣衰有樣睇姐<br />\n國安大法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9112036738bf50a014838fc37b369919d1e9fe3c","tid":2310571,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:15:41.000Z","msg":"中國人全部間諜邊洗睇樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449e9d1d0e9e0898344c73a0d5de9665b9848f6a","tid":2310571,"uid":69614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:19:48.000Z","msg":"科研成果自古以來屬於中國<br />\n間諜說法損害14億人民感情"},{"pid":"81c23de97de74a18f78bf7bfb2744e67f7eb7b45","tid":2310571,"uid":54959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:26:43.000Z","msg":"咩相由心生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b463f26170779368305ad921bd150913853035a9","tid":2310571,"uid":308251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:28:32.000Z","msg":"唔怪得中國人個個都咁樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79659a3ce3ffe2a8113d5458cfcc94c8f2c4e18","tid":2310571,"uid":227835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:29:55.000Z","msg":"唔信你都可以屈成不自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hk